<section class="guideSection">
  <h2>One Sensor vs Multiple Sensors</h2>

  <p>
    Garden beds don’t dry evenly. A single sensor only represents one location.
  </p>

  <p>
    For better coverage:
  </p>

  <ul class="plainList">
    <li>use multiple sensors in larger beds</li>
    <li>place them in representative locations</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Coverage improves accuracy.
  </p>
</section>

